org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.visitors.preprocess.strategies.wsio
Interface IAeMessageDataStrategyNames

public interface IAeMessageDataStrategyNames

Provides the names for the valid strategies for producing and consuming message data

Field Summary
static java.lang.String ELEMENT_VARIABLE
          name of the strategy where an element variable is used to produce/consume the message data (single part element message only)
static java.lang.String EMPTY_MESSAGE
          name of the strategy where the variable is not present because it's an empty message
static java.lang.String FROM_PARTS
          name of the strategy where the receive/onEvent/onMessage contains the fromParts construct which copies the message data to other variables within scope
static java.lang.String MESSAGE_VARIABLE
          name of the strategy where a message variable is used to produce/consume the message data
static java.lang.String TO_PARTS
          name of the strategy where the invoke/reply contains the toParts construct which copies other variable data into an anonymous temporary WSDL message variable
